Language: Rukai
Language code:
Lines: translit-seg gloss translat
Author: Kristen Howell
Date: January 22, 2018
Source a: Zeitoun, Elizabeth. A Grammar of Mantauran (Rukai). Institute of Linguistics, Academia Sinica, 2007. Print.

# 1
Source: a:204
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena:{}
to'aomalae li maraveravere lrao
to'a-omal-ae =li ma-raveravere =lrao
REASNMZ-sing.DYN.NF-REASNMZ 1SG.GEN STAT.FIN-be.happy 1SG.NOM
`The reason I am singing is because I am happy.'

# 2
Source: a:204
