# 6
Source: a:445
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena:{}
lo moa ta dhona amoka'ete mita
lo m-oa =ta dhona amo-ka-'ete =mita
if SUBJ-go 1PL.GEN that IRR-STAT.NF-die 1PL.NOM
`If we go there, we will die.'

# 7
Source: a:445
